HEADWORD: Rescription
<hw>Re*scrip"tion</hw> <pr>(r?-skr?p"sh?n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>rescriptio</ets>: cf. F. <ets>rescription</ets>. See
<er>Rescribe</er>.]</ety> <def>A writing back; the answering of a
